PT Mandiri AXA General Insurance Indonesia
Career OpportunitiesThe AXA Group is one of the largest insurance groups in the world. AXA operates in more than 61 countries throughout Europe, North America, Asia Pacific, Africa and Middle East serving over 95 million customers and managing funds over Euro 1 trillion. Supported by 214,000 dedicated staff and financial advisers, AXA leads the industry in terms of professionalism, trustworthiness, innovation and reputation. AXA has a multi-distribution model in Indonesia, and due to our rapid growth we are inviting professionals to fill the following position:
Heavy Equipment & Motor Vehicle Underwriting Specialist (Assistant Manager)
Jakarta Raya
Responsibilities:
Conduct underwriting assessment of Fleet Motor Vehicle & Heavy Equipment risks and deliver underwriting decisions.
Requirements:Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree or Post Graduate's Degree in Mechanical Engineering, and/or equivalent, preferably from a reputable University. At least
4 years experience in Heavy Equipment and Motor Vehicle underwriting or claim.Having experience in Heavy Equipment site survey.Have a good understanding in Heavy Equipment risk, policy clauses and wordings.Already holds an AAAIK or AAIK would be great advantage.
